# Tokens vault — plaintext-seeded encryptor + Fernet key must NEVER be
# pushed (GitHub secret scanning blocks them and they leak prod creds).
# Only the encrypted vault (tokens.md.enc) + decrypt_tokens.py are safe
# to push.
scripts/encrypt_tokens.py
download/TokenKey

